---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="VPNVerdict terms of service. Rules and guidelines for using our website.">
  <article class="legal">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span class="sep">/</span>
      <span class="current">Terms of Service</span>
    </nav>

    <header class="page-header">
      <span class="page-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      <div class="header-rule"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <section>
        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing VPNVerdict (vpnverdict.net), you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Content and Accuracy</h2>
        <p>We strive to provide accurate, up-to-date VPN reviews and comparisons. However, VPN features, pricing, and policies change frequently. We recommend verifying current details directly with the VPN provider before purchasing. Our content is for informational purposes only and does not constitute professional advice.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Affiliate Relationships</h2>
        <p>VPNVerdict participates in affiliate programs. We may earn commissions when you purchase VPN services through our links. This does not affect our editorial independence or the price you pay. See our <a href="/disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on VPNVerdict, including text, graphics, and logos, is owned by VPNVerdict and protected by copyright. You may not reproduce or distribute our content without written permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>VPNVerdict is not liable for any damages arising from your use of the site or reliance on our content. We are not responsible for the services, products, or practices of the VPN providers we review.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:info@vpnverdict.net">info@vpnverdict.net</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal { max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-400); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--ink-500); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--ink-950); }
  .sep { color: var(--ink-300); }
  .current { color: var(--ink-400); }

  .page-header { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); animation: fadeInUp var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out) both; }
  .page-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--ink-400); }
  .page-header h1 { margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
  .updated { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--ink-400); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .header-rule { height: 2px; width: 48px; background: var(--ink-950); }

  .content section { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .content h2 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); padding-top: var(--space-xl); border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-100); }
  .content section:first-child h2 { border-top: none; padding-top: 0; }
  .content p { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.75; }
  .contact a { font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
